ally helping us cover the World Cup before becoming a Junior News Editor in January 2023.\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2416, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Born in North London, Nnamdi attended Nottingham Trent University and previously worked at The Voice and the Barnet Post.Follow Nnamdi on Twitter@nnamdionye\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2573, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2425, \"end\": 2437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_London\", \"score\": 0.8790040457558634, \"rank\": 0.1347553840922181, \"text\": \"North London\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_London\"}, {\"begin\": 2466, \"end\": 2471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Trent\", \"score\": 0.9993348435758098, \"rank\": 0.0004996184114194911, \"text\": \"Trent\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Trent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Trent\"}, {\"begin\": 2508, \"end\": 2517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Voice_UK\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1043883466494293e-17, \"text\": \"The Voice\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Voice_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Voice_UK\"}, {\"begin\": 2526, \"end\": 2532, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barnet_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9992539763980165, \"rank\": 0.0007459038932203399, \"text\": \"Barnet\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barnet_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barnet_F.C.\"}]}]}"